{"tid":1471642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話民意係廢嘅情緒化撚，勇武手足入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:59:27.000Z","uid":135811,"like":32,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c768171f9d783d079c7559ed9dab5446106c7a56","tid":1471642,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"吸取教訓：日本社運失敗的歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁多位琴日機場有份狗衝嘅手足<br />\n希望大家再睇一睇呢個post<br />\n<br />\n然後痾督尿 照一照自己 反省吓自己做過乜<br />\n<br />\n咁想歷史重現冇人阻到你 但希望你係想同中共攬炒 而唔係攬住成個運動，連帶之前700個手足，5位烈士同前線所有義士攬炒<br />\n<br />\n勇武還勇武 做實事還做實事 請觀乎大局 依家係武力不對等嘅人民戰爭 唔係一寸山河一寸血嘅熱戰<br />\n<br />\n剩低嘅你明嘅"},{"pid":"d560548dc6bc4de422def1d950e7e43a20e0f277","tid":1471642,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"a17be24c81c52d26776ccd3110fb8afe02d4afc0","tid":1471642,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1b4f926bb2f81bedcb195fe63edc53d87717b449","tid":1471642,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"91b3ae3c16423103e2e2e2b1367ab87913c41d46","tid":1471642,"uid":135811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"fed3f143b30a54d95140365febf8fac095d59ad7","tid":1471642,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu